00:17:13,583 --> 00:17:15,666
OKAY, NOW LINK
YOUR ARMS TOGETHER.

435
00:17:15,750 --> 00:17:17,416
- UH... HOW COME?
- OUR ARMS?

436
00:17:17,500 --> 00:17:19,166
- WE GOT TO MAKE THIS
LOOK AUTHENTIC,

437
00:17:19,250 --> 00:17:20,833
ESPECIALLY AFTER WHAT HAPPENED,
SO DO IT.

438
00:17:20,916 --> 00:17:22,833
- I'M IN.  GIVE ME YOUR ARM.

439
00:17:22,916 --> 00:17:24,583
- IF YOU TRY TO TOUCH ME
ANYWHERE ELSE, I'LL KILL YOU.

440
00:17:27,833 --> 00:17:29,041
