THE TOP OF YOUR HEAD TO--

456
00:17:56,666 --> 00:17:59,708
- TO WHAT?
- YOUR EYEBROWS.

457
00:17:59,791 --> 00:18:02,166
- MY FOREHEAD?
I GUESS THAT MAKES SENSE.

458
00:18:06,291 --> 00:18:07,375
- I HAVE TO ASK.

459
00:18:07,458 --> 00:18:08,833
WHY ARE YOUR ARMS 
CROSSED LIKE THAT?

460
00:18:08,916 --> 00:18:12,000
- MIZUKI?
- YOU'RE SO CLOSE TO EACH OTHER.

461
00:18:12,083 --> 00:18:14,333
IT ALMOST LOOKS LIKE-- LIKE...

462
00:18:14,416 --> 00:18:17,333
LIKE THE TWO OF YOU MIGHT
BE DATING OR SOMETHING.

463
00:18:17,416 --> 00:18:20,875
- WAIT, WAS THAT LINE
IN THE SCRIPT?

464
00:18:20,958 --> 00:18:22,875
OH, SHE'S IMPROVISING.

465
00:18:22,958 --> 00:18:24,500
- YOU'RE RIGHT, MIZUKI.

466
00:18:24,583 --> 00:18:26,291
AKIHISA AND I
ARE INDEED TOGETHER.

467
00:18:26,375 --> 00:18:28,666
- WHY DIDN'T YOU
TELL ME ABOUT THIS?

468
00:18:28,750 --> 00:18:32,416
- I'M SORRY, I SHOULD
HAVE SAID SOMETHING EARLIER.

469
00:18:32,500 --> 00:18:34,041
- SO I WAS RIGHT.

470
00:18:34,125 --> 00:18:37,750
YOU REALLY HAD A THING
FOR AKIHISA THIS WHOLE TIME.

471
00:18:37,833 --> 00:18:40,250
- YES, AND I'M SORRY
FOR KEEPING THAT FROM YOU.

472
00:18:40,333 --> 00:18:42,666
ESPECIALLY SINCE
I KNEW HOW YOU FELT.

473
00:18:42,750 --> 00:18:44,083
I REALLY AM SORRY.

474
00:18:44,166 --> 00:18:45,833
PLEASE SAY YOU'LL
BE ABLE TO FORGIVE ME.

475
00:18:45,916 --> 00:18:49,166
- YOU KNOW, I SORT OF
ALREADY KNEW YOU LIKED HIM,

476
00:18:49,250 --> 00:18:51,916
BUT I DO FEEL BETTER NOW
THAT YOU'VE BEEN HONEST WITH ME.

477
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:53,250
I UNDERSTAND.

478
00:18:53,333 --> 00:18:54,791
YOU WERE IN
AN AWFUL POSITION.

479
00:18:54,875 --> 00:18:56,750
I DON'T KNOW IF I WOULD
HAVE SAID ANYTHING EITHER.

480
00:18:56,833 --> 00:18:59,291
- DOES THAT MEAN
YOU'RE GONNA FORGIVE ME?

481
00:18:59,375 --> 00:19:02,666
- THIS ISN'T ABOUT
WHETHER OR NOT I'LL FORGIVE YOU.

482
00:19:02,750 --> 00:19:04,166
I THINK YOU SHOULD
HAVE THE FREEDOM

483
00:19:04,250 --> 00:19:05,916
TO LIKE WHOMEVER 
YOU WANT TO LIKE.

484
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:08,250
AND I CAN'T FAULT
YOU FOR THAT, MINAMI,

485
00:19:08,333 --> 00:19:10,208
ANY MORE THAN
I COULD FAULT MYSELF.

486
00:19:10,291 --> 00:19:13,166
- THANK YOU.
- SURE.

487
00:19:13,250 --> 00:19:14,708
BUT STILL I--

488
00:19:14,791 --> 00:19:16,791
I CAN'T FORGIVE YOU FOR
KISSING HIM THIS MORNING.

489
00:19:16,875 --> 00:19:18,250
YOU WENT TOO FAR!
AND ON TOP OF THAT,

490
00:19:18,333 --> 00:19:20,250
YOU STOLE THE VERY FIRST KISS
HE WILL EVER HAVE.

491
00:19:20,333 --> 00:19:21,583
- BUT WE ALREADY
EXPLAINED THAT WAS

492
00:19:21,666 --> 00:19:23,083
BECAUSE OF
THE EMAIL AND STUFF.

493
00:19:23,166 --> 00:19:24,750
- DON'T YOU "AND STUFF" ME.

494
00:19:24,833 --> 00:19:26,375
GOD, MAY BE ABLE
TO LET THAT ONE GO,

495
00:19:26,458 --> 00:19:27,958
BUT I WILL NEVER FORGIVE
EITHER ONE OF YOU.

496
00:19:28,041 --> 00:19:31,875
- ( gasps )
NO, IT'S A WIRETAP THINGY.

497
00:19:31,958 --> 00:19:34,375
- YOU GUYS ARE STUPID.  STUPID!

498
00:19:34,458 --> 00:19:36,875
- IF HIMEJI SPILLS THE BEANS
WITHOUT NOTICING IT,

499
00:19:36,958 --> 00:19:38,416
MIHARU COULD FIGURE
OUT THE TRUTH.

500
00:19:39,958 --> 00:19:42,083
- HIMEJI, WAIT!
- HEY, HOLD UP!

501
00:19:42,166 --> 00:19:43,333
WHAT'S GOING ON?

502
00:19:43,416 --> 00:19:45,041
YOU DON'T HAVE
TO GO AFTER HER,

503
00:19:45,125 --> 00:19:47,166
UNLESS YOU'RE GONNA
PICK HER OVER ME.

504
00:19:47,250 --> 00:19:48,458
- I'M SORRY, MINAMI.

505
00:19:48,541 --> 00:19:51,125
BUT THERE'S SOMETHING
I HAVE TO TAKE CARE OF.

506
00:19:51,208 --> 00:19:53,458
- NO, YOU CAN'T LEAVE ME.

507
00:19:53,541 --> 00:19:56,375
AKI, PLEASE, I HAVE
SOMETHING I WANT TO TELL YOU.

508
00:19:58,000 --> 00:20:01,041
I THINK I'M
IN LOVE WITH YOU.

509
00:20:01,125 --> 00:20:06,083
FINALLY, I SAID IT.

510
00:20:09,916 --> 00:20:11,500
- WHAT THE HELL
WAS THAT ALL ABOUT?

511
00:20:11,583 --> 00:20:13,333
THERE'S A SCRIPT, YOU KNOW?

512
00:20:13,416 --> 00:20:16,458
- YEAH, DON'T WORRY.
I'M DONE ACTING.

513
00:20:16,541 --> 00:20:19,458
EVERYONE KNOWS
AKI LIKES GIRLY-GIRLS.

514
00:20:19,541 --> 00:20:21,291
SO THIS HAS JUST
BEEN A WASTE OF TIME.

515
00:20:24,750 --> 00:20:26,500
- Aki: HIMEJI.

516
00:20:30,958 --> 00:20:32,166
- OH, HI, AKIHISA.

517
00:20:41,625 --> 00:20:43,500
I DIDN'T EVEN KNOW
THAT THING WAS THERE.

518
00:20:43,583 --> 00:20:45,916
THANKS SO MUCH
FOR SAVING ME AGAIN.

519
00:20:46,000 --> 00:20:47,958
- ARE YOU FEELING OKAY, HIMEJI?

520
00:20:48,041 --> 00:20:49,958
YOU SEEM LIKE YOU MIGHT
BE A LITTLE BUMMED.

521
00:20:50,041 --> 00:20:51,458
- OH, NO, DO
I LOOK THAT BAD?

522
00:20:51,541 --> 00:20:53,833
- WELL, NOT BAD,
MAYBE A LITTLE LONELY.

523
00:20:53,916 --> 00:20:56,125
- I WONDER WHAT 
THAT LOOKS LIKE.

524
00:20:56,208 --> 00:20:58,000
