525
00:20:58,083 --> 00:20:59,958
IT'S PROBABLY BECAUSE
I'M A LITTLE SAD.

526
00:21:00,041 --> 00:21:01,500
EVEN IF IT WAS
ONLY FOR SHOW,

527
00:21:01,583 --> 00:21:03,208
