THE PERSON I LIKE

528
00:21:03,291 --> 00:21:05,083
WAS TAKEN AWAY FROM ME.

529
00:21:05,166 --> 00:21:08,000
YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN,
DON'T YOU?

530
00:21:08,083 --> 00:21:10,125
- OF COURSE I UNDERSTAND
WHAT YOU MEAN.

531
00:21:10,208 --> 00:21:11,458
YOU WERE JUST GETTING
INTO CHARACTER.

532
00:21:11,541 --> 00:21:14,083
- I GUESS THAT'S RIGHT.

533
00:21:14,166 --> 00:21:16,000
IT'S LIKE HIDEYOSHI SAID.

534
00:21:16,083 --> 00:21:18,083
- I MIGHT BE
A LITTLE JEALOUS TOO.

535
00:21:18,166 --> 00:21:19,291
- WHAT?

536
00:21:19,375 --> 00:21:20,958
- IF YOU AND MINAMI LIKED
THE SAME GUY,

537
00:21:21,041 --> 00:21:23,125
